features: 22 INCH CARRY ON LUGGAGE: With exterior dimensions of 22" x 13.5" x 9" including wheels, our small suitcase carry on meets the carry on luggage 22x14x9 airline approved requirements. Interior includes large, zippered compartments with 19.5" x 13" x 9" packing dimensions.

COSMETIC CASE: The cosmetic case keeps smaller items like toiletries and valuables close at hand, with a zippered compartment and mesh pocket. An elastic strap keeps the cosmetic case secure on the suitcase handle. Cosmetic case measures: 6" W x 12" L x 10" H.

CARRYON LUGGAGE WITH SPINNER WHEELS: Rolling carry on luggage for plane travel includes 4 spinner wheels that provide you with smooth, gliding 360 movement, a telescoping handle, stainless steel name tags, and TSA lock to secure your belongings.

TECH-FRIENDLY: The quick-access front compartment includes a padded laptop pocket, padded iPad pocket, and power bank pocket that can be integrated with the exterior USB port to charge your devices - BONUS insulated pocket to keep food cool and fresh. POWER BANK NOT INCLUDED.

HARD SHELL CARRY ON LUGGAGE SET: The impact-resistant design of our luggage carry on suitcase and cosmetic case include beveled sides to deflect hard knocks and a brushed finish that reduces scratches. Enjoy hassle-free travel with carry-on luggage that works for you.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Carry On Case with Extras
reviews.reviewText: The TravelArim Carry On Luggage is an excellent choice for travelers looking for a reliable and durable suitcase that is approved for airline carry-on requirements. With dimensions of 22×14×9 inches, this suitcase is perfect for short trips or weekend getaways.The suitcase is constructed with a hard shell that is both lightweight and durable, ensuring that your belongings will be protected during your travels. Additionally, the suitcase features spinner wheels, which make it easy to maneuver through crowded airports and busy streets.One of the standout features of this suitcase is its expandability and lockability. The main entry and flap side are both lockable, providing an added level of security for your belongings.The suitcase can also be expanded, allowing you to pack extra items as needed.The exterior flap on the suitcase can hold your laptop, iPad, or a few snacks or other electronics, which is a convenient feature for those who need easy access to these items while traveling.Although the interior side with the zipper flap is small due to the exterior flap, the expandable feature allows for extra space to pack needed items.Furthermore, for travelers who use compression bags or air flow storage bags, this suitcase will make traveling much easier.The included cosmetic case is also spacious, making it easy to pack your personal travel items or electronics.The exterior carry strap on the cosmetic case is a thoughtful addition, allowing you to easily transport your belongings.In conclusion, the TravelArim Carry On Luggage is an exceptional choice for anyone seeking a durable, lightweight, and expandable suitcase that is both secure and convenient.Its included cosmetic case is a great addition for travelers looking for extra space and organization.Overall, this luggage set is an excellent investment for any traveler.I haven't used yet but I'm looking forward to traveling with it and seeing how well it holds up to the hussle and bussle of travel life.Oh you'll have to provide your own external charge but the case does have port to plug in if needed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for traveling light
reviews.reviewText: Good quality. None of the wheels came off. Very light when unpacked. Handle easily goes up and down. Zipped up and expanded easily. The front pocket is more for a tablet. I could barely fit my work laptop in it. A slim laptop might work. Overall good value for less than $100. Fits in overhead bin easily.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Carry-on luggage just really stepped it up a notch
reviews.reviewText: In all honesty, I have not actually used the suitcase yet but I plan so at the end of the month for a trip…I spent $300 on a Solgaard check-in suitcase, and this one just blows that one out of the water.I love how the zippers can be locked in, I love the phone charging port.I read other reviews where people said their laptops wouldn’t fit. I don’t know what kind of laptop they have but mine is a 15" and it fits perfectly as does my charging bank.It rolls so smoothly.And then there’s that adorable extra case for make up, hair products, and anything else you need to put in there. and according to the product description, it’s the perfect size to slide up under the seat in front of you.If I do have end up having issues, I will post an update.

reviews.reviewText: Great carry on suitcase that more than meets the eye. A laptop and ter clearing security in the airport. Other beloved features - combo lock with TSA access. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Expandable but vanity case is small
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to travel Great Britain with only a carry on. This measures the maximum that most airlines accept. It also expands which I wanted so I could purchase a few souvenirs. At first I loved the little vanity case. However, reality is it doesn’t hold too much. I’ll use it for an shorter trip when I can share space in my suitcase for hair straighteners, etc. it’s durable, and rolls easy with four wheels. Light weight. I put the zippers to the test as I needed the expansion. Held up great! I recommend this case.
